snippet.title: Towards The Pantheon Release Trailer - Available Now On Steam & Itch.io!
snippet.description:
Check out Connor's games:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/search/?developer=Connor%20O.R.T.%20Linning
Itch.io: https://connorort.itch.io/

Check out Connor's music:
Bandcamp: https://connorortlinning.bandcamp.com/
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/0CkuyYToe6U0qoWe2VwdKU?si=swudmLEURY2uwF7yikBzsQ
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/user/ORTmusic
Amazon Music: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Connor+O.R.T.+Linning&i=digital-music&search-type=ss&ref=ntt_srch_drd_B07HFHK1LY
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/ca/artist/connor-o-r-t-linning/1436506175

Follow Connor on Twitch for gaming, game development, music composition, and speedrun livestreams:
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/connorort/

Follow Connor on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ConnorORT
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/connorort/

Donate to support Connor's work:
Paypal: https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/connorort
Kofi: https://ko-fi.com/connorort
Crypto addresses: https://pastebin.com/GL0MdEqE
* Please note that all donations are considered final.

Contact Connor via email:
connorortlinning@gmail.com 

All music recorded/performed/written by Connor O.R.T. Linning.
